title: Udi's Bread Cafe at Anschutz-Fitzsimmons
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This bread company operates several cafes in Colorado and its bread is sold in stores nationwide. Menu includes several vegetarian suitable dishes and a few vegan ones: veggie burger, falafel, Buddha bowl, and sides. All sandwiches can be made with Udi's gluten-free bread.
